snippet.title: Nerd Simulator - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Nerd Simulator is Coming!

It’s never too late to turn your life around! 💪

Learn how to earn 💵 while having fun and become independent from your mum. Step into the shoes of a 40-year-old nerd who finally decides to move out and build a life of his own in this hilarious blend of RPG and simulator gameplay! 🏠

Add to your Steam Wishlist now!
🔗https://store.steampowered.com/app/3128220/Nerd_Simulator
